text: Søren Elung Jensen (7 July 1928 - 22 January 2017) was a Danish actor. He was born in Odense. He appeared in 22 movies between 1960 and 1999. Elung Jensen died from lung cancer on 22 January 2017 in Hellerup. He was 88. ==Filmography== * Støv på hjernen (1961) * Den rige enke (1962) * Det støver stadig (1962) * Støv for alle pengene (1963) * Tænk på et tal (1969) * King Lear (1971) * Besat (1999) * Manden som ikke ville dø (1999) ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1928 births Category:2017 deaths Category:Danish movie actors Category:Danish television actors Category:Deaths from lung cancer Category:Cancer deaths in Denmark
